## This is the path for directories that wpupdate will automatically go and update. If you have multiple sites
## seperate them simply by commas. For example say I have two different blogs in /var/www/blog1 and /var/www/blog2
## if I add the line below to be /var/www/blog1,/var/www/blog2 it will iterate through the directories for you.
BLOG_PATH="/var/www"
